          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-573-ROGP-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-573-ROGP-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-573-ROGP-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">OR, THE HUE AND CRY AFTER THE ATTORNIES, GOING TO RIDE THE CIRCUIT&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-573-ROGP-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-573-ROGP-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-573-ROGP-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-573-ROGP-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-573-ROGP-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-573-ROGP-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-1" n="1">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-2" n="2">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-3" n="3">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-4" n="4">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-5" n="5">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-6" n="6">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-7" n="7">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-8" n="8">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-9" n="9">Now the active young attornies</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-10" n="10">Briskly travel on their journeys,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-11" n="11">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-12" n="12">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-13" n="13">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-14" n="14">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-15" n="15">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-16" n="16">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-17" n="17">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-18" n="18">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-19" n="19">Looking big as any giants,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-20" n="20">On the horses of their clients;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-21" n="21">Like so many little Mars's,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-22" n="22">With their tilters at their arses,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-23" n="23">Brazen hilted, lately burnished,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-24" n="24">And with harness-buckles furnished;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-25" n="25">And with whips and spurs so neat,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-26" n="26">And with jockey-coats complete;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-27" n="27">And with boots so very greasy,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-28" n="28">And with saddles eke so easy,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-29" n="29">And with bridles fine and gay,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-30" n="30">Bridles borrowed for a day,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-31" n="31">Bridles destined far to roam,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-32" n="32">Ah! never to return to home;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-33" n="33">And with hats so very big, sir,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-34" n="34">And with powdered caps and wigs, sir;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-35" n="35">And with ruffles to be shown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-36" n="36">Cambric ruffles not their own;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-37" n="37">And with holland shirts so white,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-38" n="38">Shirts becoming to the sight,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-39" n="39">Shirts bewrought with different letters,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-40" n="40">As belonging to their betters:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-41" n="41">With their pretty tinselled boxes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-42" n="42">Gotten from their dainty doxies,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-43" n="43">And with rings so very trim,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-44" n="44">Lately taken out of lim──</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-45" n="45">And with very little pence,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-46" n="46">And as very little sense:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-47" n="47">With some law but little justice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-48" n="48">Having stolen from my hostess,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-49" n="49">From the barber and the cutler,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-50" n="50">Like the soldier from the sutler;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-51" n="51">From the vintner and the tailor,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-52" n="52">Like the felon from the gaoler,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-53" n="53">Into this and t'other county,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-54" n="54">Living on the public bounty;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-55" n="55">Thorough town and thorough village,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-56" n="56">All to plunder, all to pillage;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-57" n="57">Thorough mountains, thorough valleys,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-58" n="58">Thorough stinking lanes and alleys;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-59" n="59">Some to cuckold farmers' spouses,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-60" n="60">And make merry ih their houses;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-61" n="61">Some to tumble country wenches</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-62" n="62">On their rushy beds and benches,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-63" n="63">And, if they begin a fray,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-64" n="64">Draw their swords and run away:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-65" n="65">All to murder equity,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-66" n="66">And to take a double fee;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-67" n="67">Till the people all are quiet</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-68" n="68">And forget to broil and riot,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-69" n="69">Low in pocket, cowed in courage,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-70" n="70">Safely glad to sup their porridge,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-71" n="71">And vacation's over── then</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-573-ROGP-line-72" n="72">Hey for Dublin town again!</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
